--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.2.2 (2020-11-29)
E: Define default no_proxy environment variable entries (localhost, 127.0.0.1, ::1)

* Version 1.2.1 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-09-27)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-13)
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-12)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'

* Version 0.6.2 (2018-09-09)
B: Fix YAML syntax error in template
E: Correct documentation

* Version 0.6.1 (2018-09-07)
B: Add missing 'export' statement for 'no_proxy' option

* Version 0.6.0 (2018-09-07)
F: Add support for 'no_proxy' option (shell_no_proxy)
E: Improve options to define no value (e.g. disable)

* Version 0.5.0 (2018-09-05)
F: Add support for 'https_proxy' option (shell_https_proxy)

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-01-11)
F: Add option 'shell_color_prompt' to control the shell prompt colors

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-01-05)
F: Initial release
